snippet.title: Hypnorain - Bullet Hell Shooter Trailer
snippet.description:
www.kircode.com/hypnorain - Free demo available!

Hypnorain is a vertical bullet hell shooter. 

The player guides a character through handcrafted levels, shooting and dodging their way through an army of enemies and their mesmerizing bullet patterns.
